on-status>B</classification-status><classification-data-source>H</classification-data-source><scheme-origination-code>C</scheme-origination-code></classification-cpc></main-cpc></classifications-cpc><classification-national><country>US</country><main-classification>4033224</main-classification></classification-national><invention-title id="d0e61">Quick Clamping Device</invention-title><us-parties><us-applicants><us-applicant sequence="00" app-type="applicant" designation="us-only"><addressbook><last-name>Shi</last-name><first-name>Chuanwen</first-name><address><city>Wuyang County</city><country>CN</country></address></addressbook><residence><country>CN</country></residence></us-applicant></us-applicants><inventors><inventor sequence="00" designation="us-only"><addressbook><last-name>Shi</last-name><first-name>Chuanwen</first-name><address><city>Wuyang County</city><country>CN</country></address></addressbook></inventor></inventors></us-parties><pct-or-regional-filing-data><document-id><country>WO</country><doc-number>PCT/CN2012/000515</doc-number><kind>00</kind><date>20120416</date></document-id><us-371c124-date><date>20130318</date></us-371c124-date></pct-or-regional-filing-data></us-bibliographic-data-application><abstract id="abstract"><p id="p-0001" num="0000">This invention relates to a type of quick clamping device, including a semi-circular base and a screw penetrating bottom part of said base. One end of said screw extends out of said base and is connected to an eccentric wheel via a conical shaft pin. Said eccentric wheel is provided with a handle. On said screw, a fixture block and a wedged sliding block are installed, with said wedged sliding block adjacent to said eccentric wheel and said fixture block adjacent to said wedged sliding block. Top part of one end of said base is connected to a buckle via two connecting blocks and top part of the other end of said base is connected to a top cover. A protruding block is provided on top of said top cover. Free end of said buckle is provided with a groove that matches said protruding block. All connections between top part of one end of said base and each said connecting block, between each said connecting block and said buckle, and between top part of the other end of said base and said top cover adopt movable connection using quick removal pin. Two springs are provided on upper surface of top part of one end of said base. This invention features compact structure and easy operation.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>